<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br" data-theme="light">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Podcast | <%= notebook.name %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <script>
        document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', localStorage.getItem('notion-theme') || 'light');
    </script>

    <%- include('partials/sidebar') %>

    <main class="main-content" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
        
        <div class="notion-card" style="max-width: 450px; width: 100%; text-align: center; padding: 50px 30px; border-radius: 24px; box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
            <div style="font-size: 70px; margin-bottom: 25px;">🎙️</div>
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><%= notebook.name %></h2>
            <p style="opacity: 0.5; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 40px;">Sua revisão semanal em áudio</p>

            <div style="background: var(--notion-sidebar); padding: 25px; border-radius: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
                    <button class="btn-primary" style="border-radius: 50%; width: 55px; height: 55px; font-size: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 0;">
                        ▶️
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div style="width: 100%; height: 6px; background: var(--notion-border); border-radius: 3px; margin-top: 25px; overflow: hidden;">
                    <div style="width: 40%; height: 100%; background: var(--notion-blue);"></div>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 10px; margin-top: 8px; opacity: 0.5;">
                    <span>01:24</span>
                    <span>03:45</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.6; line-height: 1.5;">
                O roteiro foi gerado cruzando todas as notas deste projeto para criar um resumo auditivo otimizado.
            </p>
        </div>

        <a href="/notebook/<%= notebook.id %>" style="margin-top: 30px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--notion-text); opacity: 0.5; font-size: 14px;">
            ← Voltar para as notas escritas
        </a>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
